headline: US judge approves new bidding terms for auction of Citgo's parent
summary: HOUSTON -A U.S federal judge in Delaware on Monday approved new terms to relaunch bidding in a complex auction of shares in the parent of Venezuela-owned refiner Citgo Petroleum, set to pay creditors...
